## Content Authoring

### Section File Format

Each section is a markdown file with YAML frontmatter:

```markdown
---
type: ComponentName   # Component from foundation
theme: dark           # Component parameter
layout: center        # Component parameter
---

### Eyebrow Text      # H3 before H1 becomes pretitle

# Main Headline       # H1 becomes title

## Subtitle           # H2 after H1 becomes subtitle

Description paragraph.

[Primary CTA](#link)
[Secondary CTA](#link2)

![Image](image.jpg)
```

### Page Structure

{{#if isMulti}}
```
sites/*/pages/
├── @header/          # Special: rendered on all pages
├── @footer/          # Special: rendered on all pages
└── [page-name]/
    ├── page.yml      # Page metadata
    └── 1-section.md  # Numbered sections
```
